11#include "logging/rtc_event_log/events/rtc_event_route_change.h"
12
13#include "absl/memory/memory.h"
14
15namespace webrtc {
16
17RtcEventRouteChange::RtcEventRouteChange(bool connected, uint32_t overhead)
18 : connected_(connected), overhead_(overhead) {}
19
20RtcEventRouteChange::RtcEventRouteChange(const RtcEventRouteChange& other)
21 : RtcEvent(other.timestamp_us_),
22 connected_(other.connected_),
23 overhead_(other.overhead_) {}
24
25RtcEventRouteChange::~RtcEventRouteChange() = default;
26
27std::unique_ptr<RtcEventRouteChange> RtcEventRouteChange::Copy() const {
28 return absl::WrapUnique<RtcEventRouteChange>(new RtcEventRouteChange(*this));
29}
30
31} // namespace webrtc
